\c 30
\s Ilathi lokutshisela impepha
\p
\v 1 Uzakwenza lelathi lokutshisela impepha\x + 37.25. 40.5. Levi 4.7. Isam. 8.3. Eks.29.7,8.\x*, ulenze ngesihlahla sesinga\x + 30.4. 25.11.\x*.
\v 2 Ubude balo bube yingalo, lobubanzi balo ingalo, lilingane inhlangothi zozine; lokuphakama kwalo kube zingalo ezimbili; impondo zalo zizavela kulo\x + 27.2.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo ulihuqe ngegolide elicwengekileyo, ingaphezulu yalo, lenhlangothi zalo ezilizingelezeleyo, lempondo zalo; wenze kulo umqolo wegolide olizingelezeleyo.
\v 4 Wenze njalo amasongo amabili egolide, ngaphansi komqolo walo, enhlangothini ezimbili zalo; wenze enhlangothini zalo zombili; azakuba zindawo zemijabo ezokulithwala ngayo\x + 25.27.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo wenze imijabo ngesihlahla sesinga, uyihuqe ngegolide.
\v 6 Uzalibeka phambi kweveyili elingasemtshokotshweni wobufakazi, phambi kwesihlalo somusa\x + 25.21,22.\x* esiphezu kobufakazi, lapho engizahlangana khona lawe.
\v 7 Njalo uAroni atshisele kulo impepha elephunga elimnandi ukusa ngokusa, eselungise izibane\x + 27.21.\x* uzayitshisa;
\v 8 lapho uAroni elumathisa izibane kusihlwa, ayitshise; yimpepha eqhubekayo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ezizukulwaneni zenu.
\v 9 Linganikeleli kulo impepha engejwayelekanga\x + Levi 10.1.\x* kumbe umnikelo wokutshiswa kumbe umnikelo wokudla; njalo lingatheli kulo umnikelo wokunathwayo.
\v 10 UAroni uzakwenza inhlawulo yokuthula empondweni zalo\x + Levi 16.18. 23.27.\x* kanye ngomnyaka, ngegazi lomnikelo wesono wezinhlawulo zokuthula\x + 29.36.\x*; kanye ngomnyaka uzakwenza inhlawulo yokuthula kulo ezizukulwaneni zenu; liyingcwelengcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\s Imali yenhlawulo yokuthula
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi yathi:
\v 12 Lapho uthatha inani lonke labantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 38.25. Nani 1.2. 26.2. 2 Sam. 24.2.\x*, njengokubalwa kwabo, bazanika ngulowo lalowo ihlawulo ngomphefumulo wakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 30.15,16. Nani 31.50. Jobe 33.24. 36.18. Hlab. 49.7.\x*, nxa ubabala; ukuze kungabi lenhlupheko phakathi kwabo\x + 12.13. 2 Sam. 24.15.\x*, nxa ubabala.
\v 13 Bazanika lokhu, wonke odlulela kwababaliweyo, ingxenye \w yeshekeli\w**, njengokweshekeli \add lendlu\add* engcwele - ishekeli \w lingamagera\w** angamatshumi amabili\x + Levi 27.25. Nani 3.47; 18.16. Hez. 45.12.\x* - ingxenye yeshekeli\x + 38.26. Mat. 17.24.\x* ngumnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 14 Wonke odlulela kwababaliweyo, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphezulu, anikele umnikelo weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 15 Abanothileyo bangadlulisi, labayanga banganciphisi ingxenye yeshekeli, lapho linikela umnikelo weN\nd kosi\nd*, ukwenzela imiphefumulo yenu inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 30.16. 30.12.\x*.
\v 16 Uzathatha imali yenhlawulo zokuthula ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, uyinikele inkonzo yethente lenhlangano\x + 38.25-31.\x*, ukuthi ibe yisikhumbuzo\x + 28.12. 39.7. Nani 16.40.\x* sabantwana bakoIsrayeli phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, ukwenzela imiphefumulo yenu inhlawulo yokuthula.
\p
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi yathi:
\v 18 Uzakwenza lenditshi yethusi\x + 38.8. 1 Kho. 7.38.\x* yokugezela elonyawo lwayo lwethusi, ukugezela \add kuyo\add*; uyibeke phakathi laphakathi kwethente lenhlangano lelathi\x + 38.8. 1 Kho. 7.38.\x*, uthele kuyo amanzi,
\v 19 njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe bagezele kuyo izandla zabo lenyawo zabo\x + 40.31,32. Hlab. 26.6.\x*.
\v 20 Nxa bengena ethenteni lenhlangano bazageza ngamanzi, ukuze bangafi, loba besondela elathini ukukhonza, ukutshisa umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 21 Ngakho bazageza izandla zabo lenyawo zabo ukuze bangafi; njalo kuzakuba kubo yisimiso esilaphakade\x + 27.21.\x*, kuye lakunzalo yakhe ezizukulwaneni zabo.
\s Amagcobo lempepha
\p
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma futhi kuMozisi yathi:
\v 23 Wena-ke, zithathele amakha aqakathekileyo\x + Ngoma 4.14. Hez. 27.22.\x*, \w imure\w** elizigelezelayo\x + Hlab. 45.8. Zaga 7.17.\x* \add elingamashekeli\add* angamakhulu amahlanu, \w lekinamoni\w** \add elilephunga\add* elimnandi\x + Zaga 7.17. Ngoma 4.14.\x* ingxenye yalokho, \add elingamashekeli\add* angamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu, \w lekalamu\w** \add elilephunga\add* elimnandi\x + Zaga 7.17. Ngoma 4.14.\x* \add elingamashekeli\add* angamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu,
\v 24 \w lekhasiya\w** \add elingamashekeli\add* angamakhulu amahlanu ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + Ngoma 4.14. Jer. 6.20; Hez. 27.19.\x*, lamafutha omhlwathi \w alihini\w**\x + 29.40.\x*;
\v 25 wenze lokhu kube ngamafutha angcwele okugcoba, amakha axutshanisiweyo njengokwenza komenzi wamakha; azakuba ngamafutha angcwele okugcoba\x + 37.29. Nani 35.25. Hlab. 89.20. 133.2.\x*.
\v 26 Uzagcoba ngawo ithente lenhlangano lomtshokotsho wobufakazi\x + 40.9. Levi 8.10. Nani 7.1.\x*,
\v 27 letafula lezitsha zalo zonke, loluthi lwesibane lezitsha zalo, lelathi lempepha,
\v 28 lelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa lezitsha zalo zonke, lenditshi yokugezela lonyawo lwayo;
\v 29 ukungcwelise ukuze kube yingcwelengcwele; loba yini okukuthintayo kuzakuba ngcwele\x + 29.37.\x*.
\v 30 Ugcobe laye uAroni lamadodana akhe\x + 29.7.\x*, ubangcwelise ukuze bangisebenzele njengabapristi.
\v 31 Ukhulume kubantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi: Lokhu kuzakuba kimi ngamafutha angcwele okugcoba ezizukulwaneni zenu;
\v 32 angabothelwa emzimbeni womuntu; njalo lingawenzi anjengawo ngokwenziwa kwawo; angcwele\x + 30.25,37.\x*, azakuba ngcwele kini.
\v 33 Loba ngubani owenza anjengawo\x + 30.38.\x*, loba ewafaka kowemzini, uzaqunywa asuke ebantwini bakibo\x + 30.38. Gen. 17.14. Eks. 12.15; 31.14. Levi 7.20,21,25,27; 17.4,9,10; 18.29; 19.8; 20.3,5,6,18; 22.3; 23.29.\x*.
\p
\v 34 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Zithathele amakha amnandi, \w isitakete\w** \w leonika\w** \w legalibanu\w**\x + 30.7; 25.6; 37.29.\x*, amakha amnandi lenhlaka ecengekileyo, kube yizabelo ezilinganayo;
\v 35 wenze kube yimpepha, amakha axutshanisiweyo njengokwenza komenzi wamakha\x + 30.25.\x*, itshwayiwe, icengekile, ingcwele;
\v 36 uchole okwayo kucolisiseke, ubeke okwayo phambi kobufakazi ethenteni lenhlangano, lapho engizahlangana khona lawe\x + 29.42.\x*; izakuba yingcwelengcwele kini\x + 30.10,29; 40.10.\x*.
\v 37 Kodwa impepha ozayenza, lingazenzeli yona njengokwenziwa kwayo\x + 30.32.\x*; izakuba ngcwele kuwe, yenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 38 Loba ngubani ozakwenza enjengayo ukuyinuka\x + 30.33.\x*, uzaqunywa asuke ebantwini bakibo.